          <p><strong>Sector:</strong> Real Estate</p>
          <p><strong>Est. Price:</strong> ~$30 (Included for yield context)</p>
        </div>
        <p>
          *(Note: Trades slightly higher but included for context)* A REIT focused on skilled nursing and assisted living facilities. Despite severe operator struggles during the pandemic, OHI maintained its massive dividend and is now seeing operator coverage ratios improve significantly as the industry normalizes.
        </p>
        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros">
            <h4>Pros</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Massive dividend yield that survived the pandemic stress test.</li>
              <li>Demographic tailwinds (aging population) support long-term demand.</li>
              <li>Operator coverage ratios are steadily recovering.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="cons">
            <h4>Cons</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Highly reliant on Medicare/Medicaid reimbursement rates.</li>
              <li>Operator bankruptcies can temporarily impact rental revenue.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" id="rank-13">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="rank-badge">13</div>
          <h3>Huntington Bancshares (HBAN)</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-stats">
          <p><strong>Sector:</strong> Financials</p>
          <p><strong>Est. Price:</strong> ~$12 - $15</p>
        </div>
        <p>
          A premier Midwest regional bank known for conservative underwriting and excellent management. It trades at an accessible price point while offering a solid dividend yield and a highly defensive balance sheet heading into potential economic uncertainty.
        </p>
        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros">
            <h4>Pros</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Extremely strong, granular deposit base.</li>
              <li>Conservative underwriting history leads to low credit losses.</li>
              <li>Reliable dividend payer.</li>
            </ul>
